Package vehicle

Class Car

java.lang.Object
vehicle.Car
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Car extends Object implements Serializable
The Car class represents a car. It implements the Serializable interface to allow it to be serialized.

    • Car

      public Car(int year, String licenseNumber, String model, FuelType fuel, double fuelConsumption, int fuelTankCapacity, int currentFuelLevel)
      Constructor for the Car class. Initializes the year, license number, model, fuel type, fuel consumption, fuel tank capacity and current fuel level to the given values.
      Parameters:
      year - the year of the car
      licenseNumber - the license number of the car
      model - the model of the car
      fuel - the fuel type of the car
      fuelConsumption - the fuel consumption of the car (in l/100km)
      fuelTankCapacity - the maximum fuel capacity of the car (in liters)
      currentFuelLevel - the current fuel level of the car (in percentage of fuelTankCapacity)
